imdb.plot outline: "Neil In Therapy," is a 4 episode web series, in which the audience serves as voyeurs into the therapy sessions between the anti-social, commitment-phobic, Chick-Fil-A and Lebron James loving, occasionally Misogynistic, Neil; and his doing-her-best to be empathetic shrink, Dr. Bates. Each session finds Neil tormented by an absurd problem, which Dr. Bates reveals to be a deep-rooted issue that her client has been too afraid to face. Does Neil have the capacity and desire to change his ways? Watch and find out!
